title: Stunning Fitted Kitchen (SOLD)
description:
This bespoke fitted kitchen exudes luxury and functionality, designed with premium integrated appliances and a thoughtful layout. It features an AEG microwave, oven, and warming drawer, seamlessly integrated for a sleek and modern aesthetic. The AEG extractor ensures excellent ventilation, while the Quooker tap and separate kitchen spray tap provide the ultimate convenience. Two Fisher & Paykel dishwashers are perfectly suited for busy households or entertaining, making clean-up effortless.


The refrigeration solutions include an AEG freezer and a large 70:30 AEG fridge freezer, offering ample storage for fresh and frozen foods. Additional features include a dedicated wine store, a unit void for a wine fridge, and another unit void ready for a cooker or AGA, allowing for customization to suit your lifestyle. With ample cupboard and drawer space, this kitchen perfectly balances practicality and sophistication, creating a stunning centerpiece for any home.
